data.description: Great opportunity to own this beautiful single family home consisting of 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, plenty of room under A/C, well maintained, ample patio to enjoy with Family and Friends. Rental income potential/Airbnb, etc. Centrally located to Hard Rock Stadium, Hard Rock Casino and 20 minutes to Fort Lauderdale Airport. Great Community and No Association. Seller contribution of $5,000 towards closing costs and/or prepaids at full asking price. This home is a must see!!
